Paysius,is,a,bitcoin,payment,service,that,allows,customers,to,use,bitcoins,to,pay,merchants,The,service,offers,zero,risk,of,chargeback,or,payment,reversal,of,any,kind,due,to,the,use,of,bitcoin,The,Paysius,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,JSON,The,API,allows,users,to,make,queries,to,get,new,bitcoin,addresses,send,bitcoins,get,bitcoin,balances,An,account,is,required,with,service,and,an,API,key,is,used,for,authentication